calculations.name: bins
calculations.tableau_expression:
IF [Edad graduante] <= 17 AND [Edad graduante] <=17
THEN "Menor de 20"

ELSEIF  [Edad graduante] >= 20 AND [Edad graduante] <=25
THEN "20-25"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduante] >= 26 AND [Edad graduante]<=30
THEN "26-30"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduante] >= 31 AND [Edad graduante] <=40
THEN "31-40"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduante] >= 41 AND [Edad graduante] <=50
THEN "41-50"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduante] >= 51 AND [Edad graduante] <=60
THEN "51-60"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduante] >= 61 AND [Edad graduante] <=69
THEN "60-69"

END
